receipt

Class Merchant

  • java.lang.Object
    • receipt.Merchant
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Merchant
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This is a simple container class for a merchant object to be used as part of a receipt managing application for my final exam in CSC 201. It is meant to store relevant data for a typical merchant (Name, phone, address...) and provide it to the receipt for display.
    Author:
    Stephen Collins
